com.ephesoft.gxt.admin.shared.constant

Class AdminSharedConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.gxt.admin.shared.constant.AdminSharedConstants

  • public final class AdminSharedConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is contains the set of constants that will be shared between Client side and server side code. This class cannot be extended or instantiated. The constants can be accessed directly. created on 29-Jul-2013
